{
  "total_duration": 530.728,
  "lines": [
    {
      "i": 0,
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 12.72,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "想象你在学校 art corner 看到一张很特别的画。大人们都在讲它代表什么、情绪多复杂，可是一个小朋友认真看了一眼，说：等一下，它是不是挂倒了？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 1,
      "start": 13.07,
      "end": 31.902,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的题目是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The best art critics"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，中文是“最佳艺术评论家”。这里的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "critic"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是专门挑毛病的人，而是 someone who looks carefully and gives an opinion，也就是认真观察、再给出判断的人。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 2,
      "start": 32.251,
      "end": 49.551,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "还有"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "modern art"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "要先讲清楚。modern art 不一定像照片一样画一个清楚的人、房子或风景。它可能用 colour、shape、line、pattern、material、mood 或 idea 来表达。我们不要把它说成“乱画”。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 3,
      "start": 49.901,
      "end": 66.893,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这课真正的笑点不是“现代艺术没价值”，而是有些人会"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "pretend"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，假装自己很懂，讲很多漂亮话；小孩子没有这个包袱，反而真的在看。妹妹只问了一个简单问题："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "But isn't it upside down?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 4,
      "start": 67.243,
      "end": 76.123,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以今天的核心是：big explanation 不一定等于 real seeing。最好的 critic，不一定用大词，而是会认真观察。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 5,
      "start": 76.473,
      "end": 93.64,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "故事从叙述者的身份开始："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I am an art student and I paint a lot of pictures."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "他是一个学艺术的学生，常常画画。房间里有画布、颜料、画笔，还有一些看起来不太像普通风景的 modern pictures。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 6,
      "start": 93.99,
      "end": 116.902,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "很多人看到 modern art，会"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "pretend that they understand modern art"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，假装自己懂。他们总是告诉你"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "what a picture is about"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。可是叙述者说，很多 picture 其实并不是 about 一个清楚的东西；它们可能只是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "pretty patterns"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，像漂亮的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "curtain material"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "一样好看。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 7,
      "start": 117.252,
      "end": 135.923,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "叙述者觉得"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "young children often appreciate modern pictures better than anyone else"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，因为孩子"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "notice more"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。他的妹妹只有 seven 岁，但她总会告诉他"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "whether my pictures are good or not"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，也就是好还是不好，她都会直接说。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 8,
      "start": 136.273,
      "end": 164.144,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "昨天妹妹进了他的房间，问："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "What are you doing?"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "他说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I'm hanging this picture on the wall. It's a new one. Do you like it?"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "妹妹认真看了一会儿："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "She looked at it critically for a moment."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "然后她说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "It's all right, but isn't it upside down?"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "叙述者再看一眼，发现："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "She was right! It was!"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 9,
      "start": 164.494,
      "end": 168.87,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "为什么标题说妹妹是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "the best art critic"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 10,
      "start": 169.22,
      "end": 174.375,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "因为她发现了别人没发现的问题：画挂倒了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 11,
      "start": 174.725,
      "end": 187.885,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "对。她不是 rude，也不是故意让哥哥难堪。她只是认真看，然后给了一个 honest opinion。一个 good critic 不是只会说坏话，而是能看见真正重要的东西。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 12,
      "start": 188.235,
      "end": 191.238,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "那课文是在笑 modern art 吗？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 13,
      "start": 191.588,
      "end": 207.268,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是。modern art 可以很认真，也可以很美。有些画不是 about a house 或 a tree，而是 about colour、shape、pattern 或 feeling。课文在开玩笑的是：有些人没有认真看，却假装自己明白。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 14,
      "start": 207.618,
      "end": 211.613,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "curtain material"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "为什么会出现？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 15,
      "start": 211.963,
      "end": 227.899,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "curtain material 是做窗帘的布。叙述者说有些画像漂亮布料一样，重点是颜色和图案，不一定要讲一个故事。这就是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "in the same way that"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "的意思：我们喜欢它们的方式相似。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 16,
      "start": 228.249,
      "end": 232.056,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "那"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "upside down"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "呢？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 17,
      "start": 232.406,
      "end": 245.486,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "upside down"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "就是上下颠倒，the top is at the bottom。最后的 punchline 要看见才好笑：大家都在解释画的意义，妹妹却先发现方向错了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 18,
      "start": 245.835,
      "end": 249.363,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I am an art student and I paint a lot of pictures."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 19,
      "start": 249.713,
      "end": 253.481,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Many people pretend that they understand modern art."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 20,
      "start": 253.831,
      "end": 256.951,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "They always tell you what a picture is 'about'."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 21,
      "start": 257.301,
      "end": 260.877,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Of course, many pictures are not 'about' anything."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 22,
      "start": 261.227,
      "end": 263.723,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "They are just pretty patterns."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 23,
      "start": 264.073,
      "end": 268.153,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "We like them in the same way that we like pretty curtain material."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 24,
      "start": 268.503,
      "end": 273.639,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I think that young children often appreciate modern pictures better than anyone else."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 25,
      "start": 273.989,
      "end": 275.981,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "They notice more."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 26,
      "start": 276.33,
      "end": 281.514,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "My sister is only seven, but she always tells me whether my pictures are good or not."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 27,
      "start": 281.864,
      "end": 284.576,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "She came into my room yesterday."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 28,
      "start": 284.926,
      "end": 287.614,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "'What are you doing?' she asked."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 29,
      "start": 287.964,
      "end": 291.372,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "'I'm hanging this picture on the wall,' I answered."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 30,
      "start": 291.722,
      "end": 295.226,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "'It's a new one. Do you like it?'"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 31,
      "start": 295.576,
      "end": 298.6,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "She looked at it critically for a moment."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 32,
      "start": 298.95,
      "end": 302.766,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "'It's all right,' she said, 'but isn't it upside down?'"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 33,
      "start": 303.116,
      "end": 305.252,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I looked at it again."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 34,
      "start": 305.601,
      "end": 309.681,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "She was right! It was!"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 35,
      "start": 310.031,
      "end": 312.599,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "critic"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第一个词："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "critic"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 36,
      "start": 312.949,
      "end": 314.461,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "critic"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "critic"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 37,
      "start": 314.811,
      "end": 332.683,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "critic"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "critic"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是认真看作品、再给出意见的人，可以评论 art、books、films 或 performances。它不是简单的“爱批评别人”。课文标题说"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "the best art critics"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，意思是最会观察艺术的人。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 38,
      "start": 333.033,
      "end": 335.784,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "pretend"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第二个词："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "pretend"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 39,
      "start": 336.134,
      "end": 337.862,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "pretend"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "pretend"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 40,
      "start": 338.212,
      "end": 354.036,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "pretend"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "pretend"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是假装，act as if something is true when it is not。课文说"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Many people pretend that they understand modern art"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，就是有些人其实没有认真看，却装作自己很懂。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 41,
      "start": 354.386,
      "end": 357.402,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "appreciate"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第三个词："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "appreciate"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 42,
      "start": 357.752,
      "end": 359.696,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "appreciate"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "appreciate"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 43,
      "start": 360.046,
      "end": 379.125,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "appreciate"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "appreciate"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是理解并欣赏某个东西的价值。你可以 appreciate a picture、a song、a good story，也可以 appreciate someone's help。课文说孩子们"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "appreciate modern pictures better than anyone else"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，因为他们更直接地观察。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 44,
      "start": 379.475,
      "end": 398.527,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的 grammar 有三块，都在帮我们看懂“观察”和“比较”。第一块是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "whether... or not"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "she always tells me whether my pictures are good or not"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。whether 后面接两种可能：good，or not good。她会告诉我到底好，还是不好。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 45,
      "start": 398.877,
      "end": 417.172,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第二块是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
